Awards:
Best Application Paper Award, IEEE PES Conference on Innovative Smart Grid Technologies - Asia (ISGT Asia), 2025; 
Best Student Paper Award, IEEE International Conference on Multimedia Information Processing and Retrieval (MIPR) 2024; 
Nanyang Innovation & Entrepreneurship Award (Team), 2020 (translational project funded by the Land Transport Authority of Singapore with the objective to convert a 12m manually driven electric bus into a safe driverless vehicle in collaboration with Volvo, Sweden. I was a co-investigator on this project and consulted the software development team.);
Best Paper Award, IEEE Real-Time Systems Symposium (RTSS), 2012; 
Best Session/Track Paper Award, IEEE/AIAA Digital Avionics Systems Conference, 2012; 
Best Student Paper Award, IEEE Real-Time and Embedded Technology and Applications Symposium (RTAS), 2011;

Recognitions:
2025 publication of a Spotlight Paper (collection of top 2.6% of submitted papers – 313 out of 12107) in ICML for work in Out-of-Distribution (OOD) detection;
Nominated by the Conference Steering/Management Committee to be the Program Chair (co-Chair) for two top-tier international CPS conferences: 1) IEEE Real-Time Systems Symposium (RTSS) held in Houston, Texas, USA, in 2022, and 2) ACM/IEEE International Conference on Cyber-Physical Systems (ICCPS) held as part of the CPSIoT Week in Irvine, California, USA, in 2025;
Nominated as an Associate Editor for ACM Transactions on Cyber-Physical Systems (since 2025) and Springer Real-Time Systems (since 2024). Both are flagship journals of the CPS community;
Nominated as a Chair of the Outreach Committee (since 2026) and Member of the Executive Committee (since 2022) for the IEEE Technical Community on Real-Time Systems (TCRTS). This organisation manages two top-tier conferences, IEEE RTSS and IEEE RTAS, for the community;
Nominated to the Steering Committee of IEEE International Conference on Embedded and Real-Time Computing Systems and Application (RTCSA) conference since 2021. This is an Asia-hosted flagship international conference of the CPS community operating since 1995;
ACM Distinguished Speaker for Special Interest Group in Embedded Systems (SIGBED), Jan. 2018 - Dec. 2020;

